member.summary:
Tries to find the given property name in the reader.

For example, to find c:

// Original position
{
  "a": "1",
  "b": {
    "c": "2"
  },
  "c":/* Final position */ "3"
}

Sets the maximum recursion depth allowed when reading JSONH.

// Max depth: 2
{
  a: {
    b: {
      // Error: Exceeded max depth
    }
  }
}

Enables/disables parsing unclosed inputs.

{
  "key": "val
